 against a green grass background." class="r-1obtnmz" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="1085c180-9447-4b6d-9819-7e7b60fc142f" class="r-wk4ovp alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>You know when you shoot 85 instead of 79 but can't explain why? Arccos breaks down every round by strokes gained so you can pinpoint exactly which part of your game is costing you. Off the tee, on approach, around the green or putting.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div class="r-s3y720" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="95e46509-d80d-47da-820c-dab926c7862e" class="r-1kg4qy7"><div data-rid="2a5e0250-9e3d-46e3-8fde-32c88468071f" class="r-ufmx6s"><div data-rid="513172d5-b226-4eab-958d-abe618f49bef" class="r-lbjktl"><div data-rid="1d3ce29e-df8f-4363-9eb3-17604018ef70" style="--replo-library-e606d4ec-d4a1-400f-9fbf-60e102022e06-styles-32026ff3-2f44-4f7a-9933-c7a9a9b6d51d-attributes-color:#56c271" class="r-slacpd"><div data-rid="3f85cdb3-f8b0-40b3-846d-ebc57d94af34" class="r-cgwyhu alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>02</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="f3785a88-3041-437e-b9f1-a40b96abd471" class="r-1chyfb3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><h2>Know Your Real Distances</h2></span></div></div><picture data-rid="51efb3d2-22b6-4cbc-9b65-1401ae975ffa" class="r-oh6epa"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5" alt="An aerial view of a golf course with a graphic overlay tracing a ball&#x27;s trajectory to the hole." class="r-1acpd94" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="6980810c-b605-4060-b5a8-db550921551f" class="r-1idryoo alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Your 7-iron doesn't always go 170 yards just because it did that one time. You usually hit it 156. But this shot is uphill and into the wind on a humid day, so it's playing much longer. You need an extra club. Arccos tracks the actual distance your ball travels every shot so you're picking clubs and planning your shots based on real numbers, not your best-case memory.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="7126da32-d35b-41c4-bc5c-04ecb396cc58" class="r-f5f0x6"><picture data-rid="e16146dd-b2f9-41c0-88cc-cf4a88ed5670" class="r-15h9c9e"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=820" media="(max-width: 640px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=1024" media="(min-width: 641px) and (max-width: 1024px)"/><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5?width=1800" media="(min-width: 1025px) and (max-width: 2400px)"/><img src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/8b73bdea-5ab8-4b3d-ae46-dc3bc485a2d5" alt="An aerial view of a golf course with a graphic overlay tracing a ball&#x27;s trajectory to the hole." class="r-20xhmr" loading="eager"/></picture></div></div></div><div class="r-1t8ykkl" data-rid="1"><div data-rid="23ded957-5a5a-4eb0-8e6b-8d7a2e1b1689" class="r-1pq684i"><div data-rid="f926746c-0d45-409e-b19f-fc7a62774b43" class="r-1hsmtsa"><picture data-rid="e9b967df-a406-4dd3-806b-6302d9d152e6" class="r-1w6l5vq"><source srcSet="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/824a366a-dafd-4375-8504-aacc62618158/589e49ff-9b82-4ba8-829b-843a011f4da1?width=820" media="(max-width: 64