nd GPS detect every shot automatically, powered by AI trained on 1.5 billion+ real golf shots. No sensors on your clubs. No phone required. Just play your round while Arccos captures everything in the background.<br><br>Your purchase includes the Arccos Air wearable, a charging case, and one year of Arccos Membership with full access to the Arccos app, including Strokes Gained Analytics, Smart Club Distances, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and more.<br><br>Compatible with iOS. Works with or without Smart Sensors.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="66ed5f96-e046-4186-9160-4229ad90d070" class="r-8up6m6" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="18b3a362-bfd9-4388-881f-f7125b55d08c" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1bbpb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-vfgyaf"><div data-rid="5613afaa-74d4-403d-bf37-e2d62aff3b09" class="r-1ef7s5n alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Shipping + Return Policy</p></span></div><div data-rid="bfeb92ef-e1bc-486c-bcf3-25f2fccb4d41" class="r-bq8396" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1v7kkvq" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1bbpb2:"><div data-rid="79e94a5a-cf15-44af-a1ff-4b9e4d125ef5" class="r-1pr3fd5"><div data-rid="31e6ebf1-d5d4-4128-8dc2-c818656cf408" class="r-158hr80 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Orders typically ship within 1-2 business days. Estimated delivery dates are provided at checkout based on your location.<br><br>All Arccos products come with a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not satisfied, you can return your product within 30 days of delivery. Customer is responsible for return shipping costs.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="565388a7-6827-4300-82b8-011e0af26d29" class="r-1l4vnq5" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d6a9d1cc-e9cc-4b7d-89f8-bf18efce589d" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1rbpb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-6e33j3"><div data-rid="a82f4803-8a98-41cc-92f4-7c931108c716" class="r-ybld41 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Do I need sensors on my clubs?</p></span></div><div data-rid="12967fb3-c3a9-4608-83fa-0fe5018a8e9d" class="r-ndpq7x" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-xsoot6" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1rbpb2:"><div data-rid="b02f9fbe-dbf7-46b6-a2a6-4d12c2ed2973" class="r-1uv322x"><div data-rid="02f57823-b746-49d5-a7dd-cdafcedd8878" class="r-131e2xz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No. Arccos Air tracks your game automatically without any sensors on your clubs. Every shot is detected by the wearable. Just play. You get full access to Strokes Gained, AI Strategy, Green Maps, and scoring insights. For the deepest club-level insights, you can add Smart Sensors at any time — but they're completely optional.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d514675a-e4e5-4239-8f91-9011b764d285" class="r-1m0n6q4" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="c8b4e7ff-402b-4aae-be56-1f7d41e596e5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R2bbpb2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-11op77n"><div data-rid="36673e40-c12c-471f-a4de-27d399c6470e" class="r-1bmr26j alc