1" class="r-1t61l0w" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="744c7c0d-24fe-4e5d-9e2f-0abde8d1c581" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R6e32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-nqxolt"><div data-rid="0c3f60eb-a18e-46fd-916f-e4ddfcce7549" class="r-xkyakv alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How does club identification work without sensors?</p></span></div><div data-rid="71ca8655-b167-48cb-9d96-6373862e498c" class="r-1a2om2h" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1fo86yj" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R6e32:"><div data-rid="6f007c8b-8055-4c0b-96b6-dd488b5084e1" class="r-17p1q3z"><div data-rid="abbfea4a-0301-4679-9f2c-93966609f080" class="r-wl6paz alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>The most important insights are strokes gained, scoring breakdowns, and personalized recommendations on where to improve. All of which is possible without tagging a single club. For club-level detail, you can turn on AI-assisted tagging to infer your club based on distance and your personal play data. Club data can be edited in a matter of seconds during or after a round. Smart Sensors provide definitive club tracking, but club tracking is completely optional and never required to get the full Arccos experience.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="7d4123f7-7386-450d-bc88-377e5747ae2e" class="r-k3rz5h" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="d339ce55-7f1c-461d-a14c-3c65000ac7ed" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rae32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1xwx6j7"><div data-rid="1cbfba63-843e-467c-af19-7bfc80b60344" class="r-hharxa alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How is Arccos Air different from Smart Sensors?</p></span></div><div data-rid="70cf80bd-28d0-4062-9478-4821aca3ed37" class="r-2rgme1" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-199w5p3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Rae32:"><div data-rid="668aa0be-cc17-4aa4-9f19-00540c778195" class="r-vqkypb"><div data-rid="de98454c-4527-41ac-9c41-2c65e5c80b75" class="r-1308pzh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Both give you access to the same game tracking features and insights. The difference is how they track. Arccos Air is a single wearable that replaces the need for your phone, Apple Watch, or sensors on your clubs. Smart Sensors attach to each club and require a phone or Apple Watch on the course, and automatically identify which club you hit on every shot. You can also use both together for a fully automatic, phone-free experience.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="98a4e441-6899-4585-8830-8f218194708b" class="r-4fdivm" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="49d392ac-b319-46d2-82f7-d5c1615cb4f4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Ree32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-roznxv"><div data-rid="3300e745-8c34-49bf-91de-3d19fc77644e" class="r-3shztq alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What's in the box?</p></span></div><div data-rid="51dd81a2-b33a-4992-9fc0-43cdccee6db3" class="r-78pfcn" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-l